NAME: MOTIVE
DESCRIPTION: The reason of rejection OR the type of card

NAME: INTEREST_RATE
DESCRIPTION: The interest rate of the customer credit card.

NAME: AMOUNT
DESCRIPTION: The amount of the credit granted to the customer.

NAME: CAT
DESCRIPTION: The annual cost of the credit granted to the customer

NAME: TXN
DESCRIPTION: The amount of each transaction for each customer.

NAME: CP
DESCRIPTION: Zip Code where the physical credit card was delivered to

NAME: DELIVERY_SCORE
DESCRIPTION: A score the customer gives to the delivery company for the delivery service.
